SUMMARY:Architectural Photography
DESCRIPTION:An intensive on architectural photography\, this workshop offers insight into BRS Sreenag’s style and how he developed his practice within the field. He traces the evolution of architectural photography over his twenty years of practice\, reflecting on key industry shifts and how they have shaped his journey. He then walks through the process of planning and executing an architectural shoot\, detailing five projects. Each project presents different strengths\, which heavily influence its unique shooting style. \nIn collaboration with:\n \n\n\nEvolution and Perspectives\nRSVPs will open Sun\, Jul 26 at 7pm.\n*Facilitator*: BRS Sreenag\n*Event Categories*: Architecture\, Photography\, Visual Arts\, Workshops
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/architectural-photography/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Architecture,Photography,Visual Arts,Workshops
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thumbnail-7.jpg
