SUMMARY:Design and the Lens
DESCRIPTION:\nA panel of three celebrated architects — Sriram Ganapathi\, Biju Kuriakose\, and Deepa Suriyaprakash — will be in conversation with BRS Sreenag. Together\, they discuss the layered relationship between architecture and photography\, exploring how rich images aid an architectural practice. \nThe discussion will be recorded as a part of Sreenag’s video series\, Everything Comes Together\, where people from the architecture\, design and photography communities share their life journeys in relation to their work. \n\n\nIn collaboration with: \n \n\n\n\nExploring the Relationship between Architecture and Photography\nRSVP here (https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdFTwxHQkSrVx-QPKJBMur8ykeWnyhA7P9xwRUyqvImJrikpQ/viewform?usp=pp_url)\n*Speakers*: Sriram Ganapathi\, Biju Kuriakose\, Deepa Suriyaprakash\, BRS Sreenag\n*Event Categories*: Architecture\, Photography\, Visual Arts
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/design-and-the-lens/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Architecture,Photography,Visual Arts
